mdRecord.dcterms:title: Photograph of Congressman Moore looking over a document with the West Virginia delegation
mdRecord.dcterms:description: Congressman Arch A. Moore, Jr. with the West Virginia delegation going over a document. They are standing in the doorway of the Speakers Lobby at the Capitol. From left to right: John M. Slack Jr. (D); Elizabeth Kee (D); Ken Hechler (D); Arch A. Moore, Jr. (R); Cleveland M. Bailey (D); and Harley Orrin Staggers (D).
